<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/jake-richards> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Jake Richards was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Ministry of Justice and as Assistant Whip, House of Commons on 7 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Rother Valley in July 2024."@en .
